‚úÖ Automatically detects new config files and adds them dynamically.
‚úÖ Avoids manual exports by setting OTELCONF dynamically at runtime.
‚úÖ Prevents duplicates, so existing configs don't get re-added.
‚úÖ Starts OpenTelemetry Collector (otelcol) with all valid configs.

